  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Study ALD-103 is a multi-site, global, data collection study designed to evaluate safety and
      efficacy of allogenic hematopoietic stem cell transplantation (allo-HSCT) in patients with
      CALD aged 17 or younger.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
